    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, delivering a linear power band up to its 8,400 RPM redline. It is equipped with a precise 6-speed manual transmission and the M Variable Differential Lock for superior corner-exit traction. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and refreshed bushings. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, ensuring the internal reciprocating assembly remains within factory tolerances. While showing minor cosmetic patina, the mechanical synchronization and thermal management systems are in excellent working order.",
      "price": 34500.0,
