    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a stellar example of a well-maintained daily driver that balances performance with everyday utility. The exterior paint retains a beautiful luster and depth, though a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper reflect its honest history on the road. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in. The upholstery shows light, natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster but remains free of tears or stains, while the dashboard and trim pieces are in excellent shape. All power features, including the sunroof, heated seats, and the infotainment system, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is robust; it has benefited from regular oil changes and a recent brake service, ensuring it drives straight and shifts smoothly. It comes with a complete set of floor mats and two sets of keys. This is a reliable, attractive car ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
